## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to October 2023, and the situation may have evolved since then. Additionally, the complexity of global supply chains and the proprietary nature of some industry data may limit the comprehensiveness of the findings. The rapidly changing geopolitical landscape and technological advancements could also influence future developments in the semiconductor industry.